Customer: Haan, aapne photo share kar diya hai kya?

Customer: Achha, main abhi process mein daal deti hoon, abhi change karwa rahi hoon main. Baki aur change to change nahi karwana hai na, kuch bhi aur kuch change.
Executive: Hmm.
Customer: Theek hai. To sir abhi main ye conversation close kar rahi hoon, ek baar mail pe jayega, ek baar yes kar dena ki mere se baat ho gayi, theek hai?
Executive: Theek hai.
Customer: Theek hai. Okay.
